RawLine: SDM_1101731506,我見你天靈蓋有奇光溢出，必定是練武奇才，這懸河劍法祕笈是無價之寶，看在你我有緣，就收你一個錢，送給你練吧！,我见你天灵盖有奇光溢出，必定是练武奇才，这悬河剑法秘笈是无价之宝，看在你我有缘，就收你一个钱，送给你练吧！

Items.mt: I see that you have a strange light coming out of your heavenly soul, you must be a martial arts genius, this manual of the hanging river sword technique is a priceless treasure, since you and I have a destiny, I'll take one money from you and give it to you to practice.
